    "T049: Create packages/styles/.storybook/manager-head.html with Google Fonts preconnect and stylesheet links. Include preconnect for https://fonts.googleapis.com (crossorigin) and https://fonts.gstatic.com (crossorigin). Include stylesheet links for Fredoka (wght@400) and Nunito (wght@400;600). Preconnect before stylesheet links for performance."
